review_blob: This is one Belgium beer you're sure to enjoy.  Strong powerful tasty delight.  Enjoy, I know I will!
Great bottle...terrible beer. At $9.99 a case I should have known better. Let Russia keep it for themselves.

A very good hoppy ale.
Wish it was available year round.  The 6.8% alcohol by volume adds a good punch.
definitely pass on this one unless you enjoy piss in a clear ottle

Why cant I get this in NYC?  A great American ESB.  Got mine through a beer club and 3 werent enough.  Had to get a few cases right away! If you like bitters go out and find this one any-which-way you can!
Not at all what I expected.  A dark beer along the lines of a Boddingtons.  What hops?

Another Great beer like Fullers ESB.  I like what I like what else can I tell you. Like Fullers I prefer it in bottles.  The fresher the better. Hop heads unite!
